# Executive Summary

This report will document the complete development process of building an AI-powered chatbot for [https://codetrainafrica.com/](https://codetrainafrica.com/). We will start with a simple static scraper and will evolve it into an intelligent agent using the CodeTrain framework (a fork of PocketFlow). The chatbot will crawl the website in real-time, will use AI to make decisions about which pages to explore, and will synthesize natural language answers.

## Key Outcomes (What We Will Achieve)

- ✅ Will build a working chatbot that will crawl [https://codetrainafrica.com/](https://codetrainafrica.com/) dynamically
- ✅ Will implement the CodeTrain framework with agent-based architecture  
- ✅ Will create both a simple HTML frontend and a FastAPI backend
- ✅ Will solve critical bugs (navigation link extraction, CORS issues)
- ✅ Will deploy working system on localhost:8000 (API) and localhost:9000 (web)

