**Use Render** - Easiest setup, all-in-one hosting, $7/month

### For Client Projects
**Use Railway + Client's Domain** - Professional appearance, $5/month

### For High-Traffic Production
**Use AWS Lambda + CloudFront** - Scales automatically, $1-10/month

### For Maximum Control
**Use DigitalOcean VPS** - Full root access, $4-24/month

# Conclusion

We will successfully build an AI-powered chatbot that:

- Will crawl [https://codetrainafrica.com/](https://codetrainafrica.com/) dynamically
- Will use CodeTrain's agent architecture
- Will provide intelligent, synthesized answers
- Will show sources and crawling statistics
- Will work via both web UI and API

**Total development time:** ~4-5 hours  
**Total cost:** $0 (will use free OpenRouter tier)  
**Code quality:** Will be production-ready with proper error handling  
**Scalability:** Will be ready for Docker deployment and cloud hosting

The system will demonstrate how modern AI frameworks (like CodeTrain) can create intelligent agents that will go beyond simple keyword matching to truly understand and explore web content.

